  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "172106f1",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "From the elbow method, we can see a bend at k=4 and k=5, before the line flattens out. To provide a more precise analysis, we will proceed with k=5 for k-means."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
