  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "51d35c91",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "From the silhouette score comparison, both start at their highest value, at k=3. However, 3 clusters are too broad to be useful. We can see both models hit a plateau at k=5."
   ]
  },
